1
00:01:24,720 --> 00:01:26,000
Here, serve the tea.

2
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,120
Miss!

3
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:29,800
Miss!

4
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:31,280
Something bad happened.

5
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,600
Today they held a clan meeting.

6
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:34,200
Madam went to the council hall alone

7
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,240
to plead for you.

8
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,200
But now they are

9
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:38,160
forcing Madam to her death.

10
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,080
What?

11
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:40,120
Hurry,

12
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:42,250
let's go to the council hall right now.

13
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,200
Miss,

14
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:44,479
please slow down.

15
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,680
If you walk this fast,

16
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,940
my legs will be ruined.

17
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,360
Come on, Aunt,

18
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:49,880
drink the tea.

19
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,160
I must save my mother.

20
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,120
What's wrong,

21
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,080
Li Nianci?

22
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,580
Are you scared?

23
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,420
Don't dare to drink it?

24
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,000
Otherwise,

25
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:06,520
let Hu Linglong drink it instead.

26
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:07,680
Aunt,

27
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,039
just drink it.

28
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:10,520
If you don't drink it,

29
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,400
won't Linglong be the one to suffer?

30
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,080
Am I right?

31
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,320
Ah, it hurts.

32
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:23,800
Someone, come!

33
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:26,680
Strip her clothes and pull her hair.

34
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,040
You have to agree

35
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:29,660
whether you want to or not.

36
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,400
Ouch.

37
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,079
You...

38
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,280
You drank it too fast.

39
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,340
You were in a hurry.

40
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,240
Long'er.

41
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:49,880
In our next life,

42
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:51,880
let's be

43
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,850
mother and daughter again.

44
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,320
Alas.

45
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,400
Wenzhong,

46
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:20,160
I've let you down.

47
00:03:32,320 --> 00:03:33,800
Mother!

48
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,200
Mother!

49
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,640
Mother, wake up!

50
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:42,480
What am I going to do alone?

51
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,640
Mother!

52
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,360
Mother!

53
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,880
Say something.

54
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:57,400
Say something, Mother.

55
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:01,760
Mother!

56
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:07,120
Li Nianci committed suicide as a sinner.

57
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:09,360
She shall not enter the ancestral shrine after death.

58
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,800
She cannot taint the dragon vein of our ancestral graves.

59
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,320
Her funeral shall be simple.

60
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,120
From today on,

61
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:15,320
Hu Wenyi will act as the head of the Hu family,

62
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:17,200
handling internal and external affairs.

63
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:20,200
In seven days, a ceremony will be held at the Hu family shrine

64
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:22,130
to officially succeed as the head.

65
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,240
Boatman!

66
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:32,880
Yes?

67
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:34,320
Where are you going, sir?

68
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,520
To Xiuning.

69
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,320
Alright.

70
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,650
Get on board.

71
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,040
Come,

72
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,020
be careful.

73
00:04:42,840 --> 00:04:43,440
Okay.

74
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,660
What are you doing?

75
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,280
Before I leave for my post,

76
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:10,880
I have one unfulfilled wish.

77
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,800
I hope to seek your help.

78
00:05:14,520 --> 00:05:15,560
What wish?

79
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,520
The former master of the Hu family,

80
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,640
there's a hidden truth behind Hu Wenzhong's death.

81
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,320
I need to go to Xiuning County nearby

82
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,450
to gather evidence.

83
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:27,200
I hope you can help me with your contacts there.

84
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:28,680
Nonsense!

85
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,080
Haven't I told you

86
00:05:31,080 --> 00:05:33,600
not to have any contact with Hu Linglong?

87
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,080
You taught me since I was a child

88
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:40,640
to finish what I start.

89
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:43,040
This is unfinished business for me.

90
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,360
If I can't fulfill it,

91
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,420
I won't be at peace.

92
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,400
If I succeed,

93
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:50,640
I'll follow your teachings in every word and deed,

94
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:51,920
do nothing reckless,

95
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,120
and put the affairs of

96
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,580
the family and country first.

97
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,440
Are you serious?

98
00:06:10,440 --> 00:06:11,720
Yes.

99
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:23,520
Congratulations, Mr. Hu, on getting what you wanted.

100
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,920
Thank you, Mr. Yamamoto.

101
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,360
Oh.

102
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,080
Just a small gift.

103
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:29,400
Thank you.

104
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:31,400
This time,

105
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,520
thanks to

106
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,840
Mr. Yamamoto's advice.

107
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:38,320
From now on,

108
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,680
we will work together.

109
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:41,560
With me as the master of the Hu family

110
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,360
and your power and connections,

111
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,280
the tea business in Qimen

112
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:47,159
will be ours.

113
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,840
As for those British merchants,

114
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,640
they are nothing to worry about.

115
00:06:54,400 --> 00:06:54,960
Mr. Hu.

116
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:55,560
Yes?

117
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,020
Speaking of cooperation,

118
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:58,860
I mentioned to you before.

119
00:06:59,080 --> 00:07:00,880
Can I have a look

120
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:03,770
at the secret recipe for Keemun black tea?

121
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,000
I have more professional people

122
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:09,320
who can help research

123
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,560
and improve Keemun black tea,

124
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:14,440
so that we can expand planting

125
00:07:14,720 --> 00:07:15,850
and increase sales.

126
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:17,840
Mr. Yamamoto,

127
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,500
no problem.

128
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,400
No problem.

129
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,360
Good.

130
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,080
Then I'll

131
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,440
wait for your good news.

132
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:23,770
Okay.

133
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:24,640
Okay.

134
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,560
By the way, Mr. Hu,

135
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,240
Yes?

136
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:31,490
you have taken the position of master.

137
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,720
It's a big event in your life.

138
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,080
Why not hold a big banquet

139
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:36,960
to celebrate?

140
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,140
Celebrate?

141
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,280
Of course we must celebrate.

142
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:43,640
Come, drink.

143
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,720
Congratulations, Master Hu.

144
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:05,320
Look,

145
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,120
Long'er's makeup

146
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:08,450
is so beautiful.

147
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,880
This skirt

148
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,760
is the one

149
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:14,760
you liked best when you were little.

150
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,760
This is the first skirt

151
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:17,760
Mother bought you.

152
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,850
Mother can't bear to let you go.

153
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,440
Row, row,

154
00:08:23,200 --> 00:08:25,120
row,

155
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:29,520
row the boat to Grandma's bridge.

156
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,240
Mother.

157
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:37,880
Mother.

158
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,480
Mother,

159
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:42,480
please say something.

160
00:08:45,240 --> 00:08:48,240
Everyone, follow me to Juxian Restaurant for a drink!

161
00:08:48,880 --> 00:08:50,040
Great!

162
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:52,320
Come, everyone!

163
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,920
Keep playing!

164
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:55,240
Oh.

165
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,520
What's going on here?

166
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,160
Oh, it's quite quiet here.

167
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,250
Why don't you

168
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,850
join us for a few drinks?

169
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:05,520
Makes sense.

170
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:07,840
Auntie died a few days too early.

171
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,280
Alas.

172
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,240
Otherwise,

173
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,880
she could have made it to today's banquet.

174
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:13,000
Hahaha.

175
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,010
Are you going or not?

176
00:09:19,800 --> 00:09:20,800
Hu Dabao,

177
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,160
you and your father will die a horrible death!

178
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:26,090
You're the ones who deserve to die!

179
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,800
Hahahaha.

180
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:29,520
I won't stoop to your level.

181
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:31,040
If you don't want to go, fine.

182
00:09:31,040 --> 00:09:33,300
Come on, keep playing outside! Let's go.

183
00:09:46,280 --> 00:09:47,160
Mr. Xu.

184
00:09:47,160 --> 00:09:48,080
Inspector Zhang,

185
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:48,600
please have a seat.

186
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,360
No need.

187
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:53,400
Please.

188
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:54,600
Sit.

189
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:58,280
Mr. Xu.

190
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,440
Your father has already explained it to me

191
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,760
in his letter.

192
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:04,560
I have found out what you asked me to investigate.

193
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:06,520
According to the pharmacy owner,

194
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,800
there is indeed someone

195
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:10,600
who often comes from Qimen to buy medicine.

196
00:10:12,040 --> 00:10:13,840
That person is...

197
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,720
Oh.

198
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,080
Long'er. Mother,

199
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,010
why are you here?

200
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:37,160
You've been helping Uncle Zhao manage the accounts these days.

201
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:38,240
It must be hard work.

202
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:38,680
Oh,

203
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,600
I made something delicious especially for you.

204
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:41,120
Guess

205
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:41,920
what it is.

206
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:43,600
Mother,

207
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,000
you know I can't smell anything.

208
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,720
Aren't you making it difficult for me?

209
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,320
Here,

210
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:49,760
your favorite black tea pastry.

211
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:55,680
It's delicious.

212
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:58,320
You're the best, Mother.

213
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,480
Are you okay?

214
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,200
Linglong.

215
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,640
Qiao Xin.

216
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,000
I want to be alone.

217
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,600
But you look...

218
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,640
I said I want to be alone.

219
00:11:18,640 --> 00:11:19,900
Can't you understand?

220
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:22,360
Whenever I see you now,

221
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:24,530
I think of how you stole my body.

222
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:27,240
I think of my running away from the wedding,

223
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:29,360
and how my mother died because of me.

224
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,040
But,

225
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:32,880
didn't you say at the ancestral hall

226
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:34,240
that it wasn't my fault?

227
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:37,240
That was because I didn't know my mother would die.

228
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:39,370
I never wanted to drag her down.

229
00:11:41,560 --> 00:11:42,600
Why didn't you just let Hu Wenyi and me

230
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:44,160
perish together?

231
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:48,060
Why do you interfere with me time and time again?

232
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,800
It all started from that day.

233
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:58,760
Everything my father said was a lie.

234
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:01,320
This is no auspicious object at all.

235
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:02,560
You

236
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,080
are also a jinx.

237
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,400
I am a jinx.

238
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:07,610
Hu Linglong.

239
00:12:07,800 --> 00:12:09,200
If it weren't for my help,

240
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,600
you wouldn't even have won the tea competition,

241
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:12,680
and you would have been kicked out of the Hu family by Hu Wenyi long ago.

242
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,960
Without my help,

243
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,560
you can't do anything right.

244
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:17,080
Help me?

245
00:12:18,520 --> 00:12:19,880
You just want to use me

246
00:12:19,880 --> 00:12:21,000
to achieve your own goals

247
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,240
and return to heaven.

248
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:24,180
Do you think I don't know that?

249
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,080
Fine.

250
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:28,250
Hu Linglong.

251
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:30,080
Since you hate me so much,

252
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:32,160
we will go our separate ways.

253
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,160
Then go.

254
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:44,000
From now on, I'll take my high road,

255
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,460
and you take your low road.

256
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:49,920
This Hu Linglong

257
00:12:50,040 --> 00:12:52,900
really doesn't know a good person when she sees one.

258
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:51,040
Mr. Xu.

259
00:13:52,680 --> 00:13:53,640
You're finally back.

260
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:54,480
Here is a letter for you.

261
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,400
It arrived three days ago,

262
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,720
but you have to receive it in person.

263
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:58,280
I heard from Madam that you'd be back today.

264
00:13:58,280 --> 00:13:59,210
She was so right.

265
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,280
The official seal of the Beiyang Fleet.
